          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到晚来养性坐蒲团。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "渴了涧下饮清泉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不戴乌纱心也安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "做一个长生不老仙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那时节临崖勒马收缰晚"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "微臣一心奔山路"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "白日里奉诵黄经卷"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "饿了吃些松柏子"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "逍遥自在观山景"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "快放微臣归山去，归山去"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放你归山，你有三件大事，千万不可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪三件大事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一件，你家园好；第二件，妻又姣；第三件，儿女成双。有此三件也归不得"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山，也学不得道，可以不必归山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "万岁爷坐金殿龙耳听道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一桩桩一件件奏与当朝："
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家园好比惹祸苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "妻妾好比斩人刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哪有儿女替他死这遭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "武将捶胸泪滔滔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "就是微臣心也焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么微臣的家园好"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "什么妻来什么妾"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "未央宫里韩信死"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "文官拍手哈哈笑"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "纷纷议论不一定"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爱卿所奏何事，朕不依从？冷淡卿心，也是有的，朕也知道。再陪孤家几载，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人难舍干国忠臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "微臣情愿留下幞头象简，归山去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双手破开生死路，翻身跳出是非门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张良下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张良归山辞高皇，范蠡游湖别越王。他人不是嫌官小，见斩韩信三齐王。"
        }
